title: True North
description: True North is a SWF Wabbajack modlist of over 1000 mods that bundles 14+ years of incredible work done by the skyrim modding community into one cohesive, optimized experience. It stays true to Skyrimâ€™s spirit while improving everything: fully voiced player dialogue, overhauled quests, integrated survival mechanics (Shut off survival mode improved if its not your thing), new seasons, weather types to experience and a dynamic world that responds to your actions. Combat has been completely rebuilt with BFCO, Precision, smarter AI. Dismembering Framework, Core Impact Framework (and more). Despite its scale, True North maintains smooth 60 FPS even on a 8gb GPU.
author: Truman
